==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: There are people beyond (this) person, and skies beyond (this) sky.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: rén wài yŏu rén, tīan wài yŏu tīan

===Phrase===
'''[[人]][[外]][[有]][[人]]，[[天]][[外]][[有]][[天]]'''

# (''idiom'') No matter how good you think you are, there is always someone out there that is better.

